	<description>
		<![CDATA[
		<div align="center">
			<div class="alert alert-success" style="background-color:#DFF0D8;border-color:#D6E9C6;color: #468847;padding: 1px 0;">
				
				<h4><a href="https://www.buildal.ug/work/">University and School Joomla template - Teresa</a></h4>
				
				<p><a href="https://www.buildal.ug/work/" title="">Home</a> | <a href="https://www.buildal.ug/work/" title="">Demo</a> | <a href="//www.buildal.ug/documentation/joomla-templates/ja-athena" title="">Document</a></p>

				<p>Teresa is a perfect Joomla template for schools, colleges, universities or any educational institute's website. Supports Joomla 4, built with T4 Framework, integrates Bootstrap 5.</p>

				<p><span style="color:#FF0000">Note: Teresa requires T4 plugin to be installed and enabled.</span></p>
				<p>Copyright 2004 - 2022 <a href='http://www.buildal.ug/' title='Visit buildal.ug!'>buildal.ug</a>.</p>
			</div>
			<style>table.adminform{width: 100%;}</style>
		</div>
		]]>
	</description>

